  "title": "Receptionist (Beauty Salon) | Up to $2500 | 5.5 Days - ZH",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Up to $2,500<br />Working Hours: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM (5.5 Working Days)<br />Location: Serangoon Garden / East Coast / Great World  (Rotation across 3 outlets, 2 days each)</p><p> Key Duties:</p><p><ul><li>Greet customers warmly and assist with appointments, walk-ins, and inquiries for smooth client flow.</li><li> Handle phone calls, WhatsApp messages, and online booking platforms professionally.</li><li>Manage front desk operations – payment processing, issuing receipts & preparing daily sales reports.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and professional presentation of the reception and waiting areas.</li></ul></p><p>   Key Requirements :</p><p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in customer service or front desk is highly advantageous.</li><li>Proficient in booking platforms & POS systems to manage appointments and transactions.</li><li>Must be comfortable working on weekends & Public Holidays.</li><li>Tech Savvy</li></ul><p>WhatsApp me at wa.me/6587801169 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Sim Shu Hui Reg No.: R25129789<br />Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 23C1449</p><p></p><p></p></p>",
